						<h1>
															Fix Joomla Hack and Upgrade for Security									</h1>
			
																
				
					<div style='font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:-10px; padding-top:5px;'>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by Jacob Nicholson</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>19,925</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Nov 8, 2013'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Feb 21, 2014</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Comments:</span> <a href='#comments'>2</a></div>
