<p>We also recommend checking up on the latest <a href="http://feeds.joomla.org/JoomlaSecurityNews" target="_blank">Joomla Security news</a> which covers recent exploits discovered in the Joomla core, and also the <a href="http://feeds.joomla.org/JoomlaSecurityVulnerableExtensions" target="_blank">vunerable Joomla extensions</a> which have been discovered recently.</p>
